#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Ambapālivagga"
msgstr "1. In Ambapālī’s Wood"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Sālasutta → sālāsuttaṃ (bj) | sallaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn47.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Sālasutta"
msgstr "4. At Sālā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.4:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati sālāya brāhmaṇagāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans near the "
"brahmin village of Sālā."

msgctxt "sn47.4:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi … pe … etadavoca:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.4:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, te vo, bhikkhave, bhikkhū catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvanāya "
"samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, those mendicants who are junior—recently gone forth, newly come "
"to this teaching and training—should be encouraged, supported, and "
"established in the four kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.4:2.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Etha tumhe, āvuso, kāye kāyānupassino viharatha ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, kāyassa yathābhūtaṃ ñāṇāya;"
msgstr ""
"Please, reverends, meditate observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, at "
"one, with minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to "
"truly know the body."

msgctxt "sn47.4:2.4"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassino viharatha ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, vedanānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ ñāṇāya;"
msgstr ""
"Meditate observing an aspect of feelings—keen, aware, at one, with minds "
"that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to truly know "
"feelings."

msgctxt "sn47.4:2.5"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassino viharatha ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā vippasannacittā "
"samāhitā ekaggacittā, cittassa yathābhūtaṃ ñāṇāya;"
msgstr ""
"Meditate observing an aspect of the mind—keen, aware, at one, with minds "
"that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to truly know the "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn47.4:2.6"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassino viharatha ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, dhammānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ ñāṇāya."
msgstr ""
"Meditate observing an aspect of principles—keen, aware, at one, with minds "
"that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to truly know "
"principles."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.145"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.4:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yepi te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū sekhā appattamānasā anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ "
"patthayamānā viharanti, tepi kāye kāyānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā "
"ekodibhūtā vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, kāyassa pariññāya;"
msgstr ""
"Those mendicants who are trainees—who haven’t achieved their heart’s desire, "
"but live aspiring to the supreme sanctuary—also meditate observing an aspect "
"of the body—keen, aware, at one, minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, "
"and unified, so as to fully understand the body."

msgctxt "sn47.4:3.2"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, vedanānaṃ pariññāya;"
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of feelings—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to fully "
"understand feelings."

msgctxt "sn47.4:3.3"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā vippasannacittā "
"samāhitā ekaggacittā, cittassa pariññāya;"
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of the mind—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to fully "
"understand the mind."

msgctxt "sn47.4:3.4"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, dhammānaṃ pariññāya."
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of principles—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, so as to fully "
"understand principles."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.4:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yepi te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū arahanto khīṇāsavā vusitavanto katakaraṇīyā "
"ohitabhārā anuppattasadatthā parikkhīṇabhavasaṃyojanā sammadaññāvimuttā, "
"tepi kāye kāyānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, kāyena visaṃyuttā;"
msgstr ""
"Those mendicants who are perfected—who have ended the defilements, completed "
"the spiritual journey, done what had to be done, laid down the burden, "
"achieved their own goal, utterly ended the fetters of rebirth, and are "
"rightly freed through enlightenment—also meditate observing an aspect of the "
"body—keen, aware, at one, with minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, "
"and unified, detached from the body."

msgctxt "sn47.4:4.2"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, vedanāhi visaṃyuttā;"
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of feelings—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, detached from "
"feelings."

msgctxt "sn47.4:4.3"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā vippasannacittā "
"samāhitā ekaggacittā, cittena visaṃyuttā;"
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of the mind—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, detached from the "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn47.4:4.4"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassino viharanti ātāpino sampajānā ekodibhūtā "
"vippasannacittā samāhitā ekaggacittā, dhammehi visaṃyuttā."
msgstr ""
"They meditate observing an aspect of principles—keen, aware, at one, with "
"minds that are clear, immersed in samādhi, and unified, detached from "
"principles."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.4:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yepi te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, te vo, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imesaṃ catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ "
"bhāvanāya samādapetabbā nivesetabbā patiṭṭhāpetabbā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Those mendicants who are junior—recently gone forth, newly come to this "
"teaching and training—should be encouraged, supported, and established in "
"these four kinds of mindfulness meditation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.4:5.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
